name: Adam Marciniak
text: Great Pizza Hut. Fast Service. Friendly Employees. They have always gotten my orders correct whether they were called in or placed online. All of the food I have ordered has been good. While it is not the best pizza place in the area, it is reliable and has longer business hours.

name: Lawrence Hanson
text: This location is a bit on the small side, but the drive up window is nice. There has not been any problem that they are unwilling to solve. The staff here is friendly and polite, even when faced with escalated customers. â€¦More

name: trujello
text: If you like Pizza Hut this place is great. They always get your order right, delivery is fast, people are friendly. And you just can't beat a pepperoni lovers pan pizza.

name: S Pierce
text: I had a very patient manager who worked hard for me to get my gift card to work, it was awesome. Wonderful pizza! I came back a few hours later for a huge cookie yum!

name: John Fuson
text: First time I tried deliver it took 1.5 hours to get pizza's. This time I decided to carry out so far I've been waiting 45 mins. No good.

name: Alan Jones
text: On repeated occasions my wife and I have found this location to be chintzy and skimpy on their ingredients (I've had it!); they do, however, frequently offer good deals. Nevertheless, I'm not going to patronize this location anymore; unfortunately they are the closest of any Pizza Hut in my area. Oh well . . .

name: Scott Thomas
text: It was ok I guess, they just got it wrong. Light sauce and extra cheese but I got light cheese and extra sauce. Very annoying

name: Catherine Taryle
text: Staff were friendly, fun, obviously having a good time while doing their jobs.   I enjoyed the atmosphere created by employees so much I've gone out of my way to return, and I can count on my food consistently tasting the way I expect.

name: Melissa Romero
text: This location us less than .2 miles from a dominos location. You can see the dominos from their curbside but they do not deliver to my house... what a joke.. the reason i do not buy from them..

name: Tom Treptau
text: 4 large pizza's, all tasted good but the didn't make the effort to cut them properly.

name: Stefan Funkhouser
text: Pretty basic. You order a pizza from here and it arrives. Nothing exceptional about it, it's Pizza Hut. Obviously you are not seeking anything spectacular here.

name: All In
text:
You're reading a review for Pizza Hut? Go eat some real food! Place is nasty.
Wake up

name: Michelle W
text: They produce a consistent product. Staff is friendly.

name: Brett Kelly
text: Ordered two pizzas, cinna sticks and wings. Never got the cinna sticks or wings. Pizza was burnt and cold at the same time. Was having a party and nobody could stand to even take a bite. Don't ever order here!

name: Jonathan Adcox
text: Fast and friendly ready when I get there

name: Abhay Natu
text: Friendly staff. They do make an occasional mistake but are quick to fix it.

name: Bruce Randall
text: Carry out on time to 20 minutes late

name: Randy William
text: Love the people there and the food is good

name: Clayton O'Neil
text: pizza is getting worse every time i order one...

name: Leslie K.
text: It has been closed down..

name: Sunil
text: Like the pizza here :)

name: Richard Rotte
text: As ordered and on time.  Ready when I got there.

name: Mike Allred
text: Hey, it's pizza

name: Kyle Haynam
text: Good service.

name: Steven Daryl
text: Great Service!
